snippet.title: Age of Empires 3 The WarChiefs Gameplay HD 720p
snippet.description:
Age of Empires 3 The WarChiefs Gameplay HD 720p
PC Test Bed:
- Processor: Intel Core 2 Duo E8400 3.0GHz
- RAM: 4GB DDR2
- Mobo: LGA 775 P35 Chipset
- VGA: AMD Radeon HD 5870 1GB  Gddr5
- OS: Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 64bit
- Monitor: 19" LED

FPS without recording should be higher and smoother :D
You can lower the resolution for better fps
I make videos for fun. If you like them, that's cool, if you don't, that's cool too...
